            <listBibl>
               <bibl>Amundsen L, OMich I, 134, 1935, Pl. IV -- BL VIII, 526 (l. 1; date). - L. 5: epibole(s) katag(ogon)(?) is dubious; in unpublished notes, H.C. Youtie thought of: epibole(s) kat'a(ndra) or kat'ar(ouran), and of: epikth(niton) kata(boles). (PH)</bibl>
               
